<p><br></p><p><span style="color: rgb(112, 48, 160); font-size: 14px;"><strong>“活动现场热度涨，激情绽放在心间”</strong></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">帷幕缓缓拉开</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">灯光如梦幻般洒落在舞台上</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">台下座无虚席</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">同学们的脸上洋溢着期待与兴奋</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">在笑声与欢呼声中</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(112, 48, 160); font-size: 14px;"><strong>江西软件职业技术大学</strong></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(112, 48, 160); font-size: 14px;"><strong>第十八届校园文化艺术节</strong></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(112, 48, 160); font-size: 14px;"><strong>暨第九届创客嘉年华</strong></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">正式拉开序幕</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2.13333em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong>此次活动以“艺韵飞扬二十载，创客筑梦新征程“为主题，既展现了我校二十年的辉煌历程，也展现了我校对未来“乘势而上创伟业，接续奋斗谱新篇”的坚定决心。此次盛典，不仅为我们的视觉、听觉带来洗礼，更为我们新时代大学生提供了一个展现自我、超越自我的舞台，增进彼此间的友谊。这是一场青春的盛宴，每个人都在其中绽放着属于他们的自信光芒。</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2.13333em; text-align: justify;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746522009464.png" alt="1746522009464.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746522009464.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2.13333em; text-align: justify;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521998996.png" alt="1746521998996.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521998996.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2.13333em; text-align: justify;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521987059.png" alt="1746521987059.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521987059.png" style="width: 100%;"><br></p><p><span style="font-size: 24px;"><strong>开场</strong></span></p><p><br></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong>开场的《旗开得胜》</strong></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">每一次旗帜的挥舞，</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">都激扬着每位师生心中那不灭的梦想。</span></p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521968269.png" alt="1746521968269.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521968269.png" style="width: 100%;"/><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521962293.png" alt="1746521962293.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521962293.png" style="width: 100%;"/></p><p><span style="font-size: 24px;"><strong>青春之歌奏蓝图</strong></span></p><p><br></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">第二幕</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong>我们迎来了“青春篇章”</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">每一场的表演都对青春的描述</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">每一声欢笑都是对梦想的追逐与认同</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">让我们在此次嘉年华中以青春之歌</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">奏响属于我们自己的理想蓝图</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521950741.png" alt="1746521950741.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521950741.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521944260.png" alt="1746521944260.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521944260.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521938291.png" alt="1746521938291.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521938291.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521932238.png" alt="1746521932238.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521932238.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521926331.png" alt="1746521926331.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521926331.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521920333.png" alt="1746521920333.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521920333.png" style="width: 100%;"/></p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521913321.png" alt="1746521913321.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521913321.png" style="width: 100%;"/></p><p><span style="font-size: 24px;"><strong>悠悠文墨贯古今</strong></span></p><p><br></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">紧接着我们开启了文化的盛典</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">在这里我们传千年之经义</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">燃万古之明灯</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">在这里我们感受到了</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong>生于华夏的无比自豪</strong></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(112, 48, 160); font-size: 14px;"><strong>热爱祖国的无比深沉</strong></span></p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521874482.png" alt="1746521874482.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521874482.png" style="width: 100%;"/><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521882015.png" alt="1746521882015.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521882015.png" style="width: 100%;"/><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521888996.png" alt="1746521888996.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521888996.png" style="width: 100%;"/><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521894644.png" alt="1746521894644.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521894644.png" style="width: 100%;"/></p><p><span style="font-size: 24px;"><strong>二十载共迎新征程</strong></span></p><p><br></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(112, 48, 160);"><strong><br></strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong>“启航新征程”里每一帧的细节</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">都记录着江西软件大学二十载的风风雨雨</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">是我们对未来拼搏逐梦的决心与热情</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong>神秘嘉宾陈方平执行理事长亲自献唱《当你》</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">将现场气氛拉上高潮！</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br></p><p><span style="font-size: 24px;"><strong>谢幕</strong></span><span style="font-size: 15px;"><br></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong>由《明天会更好》这首歌结尾</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">寓意着江西软件大学的未来将更加辉煌</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">而江西软件大学学子们的未来也将更加璀璨</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">愿各位心存希冀，目有繁星</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">追光而遇，沐光而行</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521840277.png" alt="1746521840277.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521840277.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521833097.png" alt="1746521833097.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521833097.png" style="width: 100%;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><br></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521826902.png" alt="1746521826902.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521826902.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521817842.png" alt="1746521817842.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521817842.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521810913.png" alt="1746521810913.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521810913.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521804349.png" alt="1746521804349.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521804349.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><em><strong>HAPPYNIGHT、</strong></em></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521796532.png" alt="1746521796532.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521796532.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521790256.png" alt="1746521790256.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521790256.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521781965.png" alt="1746521781965.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521781965.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521771133.png" alt="1746521771133.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521771133.png" style="width: 100%;"/></p><p><br></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">校园，是青春的舞台</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">表演，是梦想的绽放</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">在热烈的掌声中</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong>旭光飞龙翱翔于会场上方</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">点燃晚会最后的激情</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">将晚会推进尾声</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(112, 48, 160); font-size: 14px;"><strong>大家齐唱《生日快乐歌》</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(112, 48, 160); font-size: 14px;"><strong>共同庆祝母校建校20周年</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">送出最美的生日祝福</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br></p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521757620.png" alt="1746521757620.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521757620.png" style="width: 100%;"/></p><p>♬..♩~ ♫. ♪..</p><p style="text-align: left;">♬..♩~ ♫. ♪..</p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong>随着“游行开始“的宣布</strong></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">学子们带着梦想与激情</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong>一起随花车开始巡游</strong></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">每个人脸上都洋溢着幸福与喜悦</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(112, 48, 160); font-size: 14px;"><strong>向着梦想奋发前进</strong></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(112, 48, 160); font-size: 14px;"><strong>共同谱写江西软件大学青春篇章</strong></span></p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521724661.png" alt="1746521724661.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521724661.png" style="width: 100%;"/><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521718021.png" alt="1746521718021.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521718021.png" style="width: 100%;"/></p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521701991.png" alt="1746521701991.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521701991.png" style="width: 100%;"/></p><p><br></p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521693275.png" alt="1746521693275.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521693275.png" style="width: 100%;"/></p><p><br></p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521684302.png" alt="1746521684302.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521684302.png" style="width: 100%;"/></p><p><br></p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521678024.png" alt="1746521678024.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521678024.png" style="width: 100%;"/></p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521670174.png" alt="1746521670174.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521670174.png" style="width: 100%;"/></p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521662800.png" alt="1746521662800.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521662800.png" style="width: 100%;"/></p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521655686.png" alt="1746521655686.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746521655686.png" style="width: 100%;"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">青春无价 热情可贵</span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">愿同学们不负韶华☝️</span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">心有无限希望 勇敢追求</span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">心怀无限热忱 大胆展示</span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="color: rgb(116, 46, 150); font-size: 14px;"><strong>在各自的舞台上熠熠生辉</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="color: rgb(116, 46, 150); font-size: 14px;"><strong>点燃内心的“passion”火苗<br>让每一天都“燃起来”！🙌🎉<br>奔走在我们热爱的道路上🥰</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><br></p>